race.comment: TOOMUCHINFORMATION (6) has a host of gear changes for this and returns from a let-up. Failed to run the 1450m out when a plugging eighth at Muswellbrook. Goes close in this grade. SHOOT THE DIVA (11) drops a few levels here after struggling in the going when fifth over 1315m at Coffs Harbour. On the backup and the drop in trip will help. SAVVYROCKER (5) back in her right class when performed above expectations to salute over 1006m at Port Macquarie. In a leading yard and goes close. JO JO SUN (4) massive jump in grade when a fading last to the smart Bartolf over 1300m at Warwick Farm in BM72 class. Set to bounce back.
